   "source": [
    "We first fitted $\\beta,\\sigma,\\gamma$ using a 3-parameter grid search that minimizes\n",
    "$\\mathrm{SSE}=\\sum (I_{\\mathrm{obs}}-I_{\\mathrm{model}})^2$. We used the ranges/resolution from `seir_grid_search.html`:\n",
